  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Have you ever imagined waking up one day to find yourself transported to a world filled with magic and strange creatures, embarking on a thrilling adventure?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Have you ever fantasized about playing different roles in this world, either as a hero defending it or as a villain destroying it?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, the opportunity has arrived! Enter the God Chosen Place!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meticulously Crafted Script</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To ensure you experience a range of emotions in the game—whether it’s excitement, sadness, joy, or heroism—I have repeatedly revised the outline. Each part of the story has been carefully considered for its logic and potential for development.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the story, you will meet characters with different personalities. Some will become your friends, while others will become your enemies. If you observe closely, you’ll discover that villains are not inherently evil; they may have pasts unknown to others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/41809a18c9b8685e3b49c8da3c9d564e.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/41809a18c9b8685e3b49c8da3c9d564e.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/41809a18c9b8685e3b49c8da3c9d564e.mp4?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make Your Choice</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the story, you will encounter many choices. Some may seem insignificant, while others could impact the plot later on. A small decision might change a character’s fate, but who knows? Perhaps that seemingly trivial choice will alter everything in the God Chosen Place…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/2a9730a36d4274e624c27a39b9403bec.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/2a9730a36d4274e624c27a39b9403bec.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/2a9730a36d4274e624c27a39b9403bec.mp4?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Easy-to-Learn Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and easy-to-learn turn-based combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your magic, buy your items, and in battle, just click to use them. Too much hassle to click? No problem, pressing a button on your keyboard works just as well!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What if you encounter an enemy you can’t defeat? Hmm… then fight weaker enemies to level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/188fab2fe0e133815d264945de212bba.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/188fab2fe0e133815d264945de212bba.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/188fab2fe0e133815d264945de212bba.mp4?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Manage Your Organization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Is the story too intense? Too sad? No way! I need a break!</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit NPCs and have them work for you to earn more gold. Why earn gold? As the saying goes, “A man without lofty ambitions is like a bird without wings!” With gold, you can recruit more mercenaries! With more mercenaries, you can conquer territories in the Fierce Battlefield! Train them and turn them into a formidable army!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Worried that managing might be too complicated?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t be! To let you better experience the ups and downs of the story, the management part is simplified for easy management!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/63cc65b5fc929e146b35eae6b9fb3cdd.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/63cc65b5fc929e146b35eae6b9fb3cdd.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/63cc65b5fc929e146b35eae6b9fb3cdd.mp4?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relaxing and Fun Mini-Games</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features numerous mini-games. Spend your free time hunting, singing, drinking, honing your swordsmanship, or running. While relaxing, you can also earn more gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/8fcd4c6e2da69a7c402e30b4873ec1c4.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/8fcd4c6e2da69a7c402e30b4873ec1c4.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/8fcd4c6e2da69a7c402e30b4873ec1c4.mp4?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Easy Map Navigation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just click your mouse to move to your desired location on the large map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/30c3fca801e71a7d2716d6b01b92c19f.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/30c3fca801e71a7d2716d6b01b92c19f.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/30c3fca801e71a7d2716d6b01b92c19f.mp4?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
