Too sad? No way! I need a break!</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit NPCs and have them work for you to earn more gold. Why earn gold? As the saying goes, “A man without lofty ambitions is like a bird without wings!” With gold, you can recruit more mercenaries! With more mercenaries, you can conquer territories in the Fierce Battlefield! Train them and turn them into a formidable army!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Worried that managing might be too complicated?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t be! To let you better experience the ups and downs of the story, the management part is simplified for easy management!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/63cc65b5fc929e146b35eae6b9fb3cdd.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/63cc65b5fc929e146b35eae6b9fb3cdd.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/63cc65b5fc929e146b35eae6b9fb3cdd.mp4?t=1733616684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relaxing and Fun Mini-Games</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features numerous mini-games. Spend your free time hunting, singing, drinking, honing your swordsmanship, or running. While relaxing, you can also earn more gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/8fcd4c6e2da69a7c402e30b4873ec1c4.poster.avif?t=1733616684\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/8fcd4c6e2da69a7c402e30b4873ec1c4.webm?t=1733616684\" type=\